FBIS4-60211 "drnes099_j_94039" FBIS-NES-94-099 Daily Report 22 May 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen Phones Amir of Qatar Phones Amir of Qatar JN2205210094 Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network in Arabic 2000 GMT 22 May 94 JN2205210094 Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network Arabic BFN [Text] Brother 'Ali 'Abdallah Salih, chairman of the Presidential Council, has phoned the Amir of Qatar, Shaykh Khalifah Bin-Hamad Al Thani, to extend greetings of the blessed 'Id al-Adha. The brother president updated Shaykh Khalifah on Yemeni developments in light of the secessionist decision by the renegade traitor al-Bid. [words indistinct] Qatar's principled and consistent stand in support of Yemen's unity and legitimacy. The brother president applauded the genuine and pan-Arab attitude of brothers in Qatar, led by His Highness Shaykh Khalifah Bin-Hamad Al Thani and his heir apparent Shaykh Hamad Bin-Khalifah Al Thani, toward Yemeni unity as a gain for the entire Arab nation. He emphasized that our Yemeni people and Armed Forces will take on all challenges.
